        <li><strong>Sell information to third-party providers with your permission</strong>. After obtaining your permission, we may sell your information to third parties who will also try to meet your needs. These third parties may be other insurance agencies, insurance carriers, financial services providers, or other entities that facilitate the process of connecting customers with financial services providers. These third parties, or the entities they work with, may contact you based on the consent you have provided.</li>
        <li><strong>As Part of a Corporate Change</strong>. We may disclose and transfer information about you to a third party as part of, or in preparation for, a change of control, restructuring, corporate change, or sale or transfer of assets.</li>
        <li><strong>For Legal Reasons</strong>. We reserve the right to transfer or disclose information about you to third parties for certain legal purposes as described above.</li>
